headline: Nauticus Robotics (KITT) Aquanaut Mark 2 Reaches 2,300m Depth in Louisiana Test
summary: Nauticus Robotics, Inc. (NASDAQ:KITT) is one of the 15 Best Robotics Stocks to Buy Under $20. On August 26, 2025, Nauticus Robotics, Inc. (NASDAQ:KITT) reported that its Aquanaut Mark 2 underwater vehicle had been tested 240 kilometers off the coast of Louisiana and reached a record depth of 2,300 meters.
